1. *Niste* znali da ćete biti ovde. (You didn't know that you would be here.)
2. *Nije* bilo nikoga koga bih mogao da pitam. (There was nobody I could ask.)
3. *Nijesmo* bili sigurni da li ćemo dobiti odgovor. (We weren't sure we'd get an answer.)
4. *Nijesu* nam ništa rekli. (They didn't tell us anything.)
5. *Niste* nas pratili. (You weren't following us.)